'''Domain Choka''' was a [[Domain]] among the [[Warrior caste]] of the [[Yuuzhan Vong]], often noted for its many skilled and cunning warriors. The most famous member of Domain Choka was [[Nas Choka]], [[Supreme Commander (Yuuzhan Vong rank)|Supreme Commander]] of the [[Yuuzhan Vong fleet]] and the final [[Warmaster]] of the [[Yuuzhan Vong]]. Other warriors included [[Shok Choka]] and [[Ushk Choka]].

